note: 
 sloth depends on the standard libc6 development libraries. specifically
  <stdio.h>
  <unistd.h>
  <stdlib.h>
  <wait.h>
  <sys/ptrace.h>
  <sys/types.h>
  <sys/time.h>

 When I figure out all the conftool stuff, I'll make a proper configure
 script. :)
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

* INSTALL:
	(as root)
	# make install 

* REMOVE:
	(as root)
	# make remove

